<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/14879229-kj"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1633266527i/14879229._UY100_CR38,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/14879229-kj">KJ</a>
