              <span id="reviewTextContainer2365371384" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11397849222933205065">This was one of my favorite Alex Cross books yet. I loved the vampire crime plot! I’m a fantasy&amp; sci-fi book genre fan so it really excited me to read this one. As for the Mastermind crime plot, I was glad it didn’t extend into further books where Alex would not know who the Mastermind was because I feel like that would have became overdone. The suspense of him finding out was just right, in my opinion. It will be interesting to see where he goes career wise. <br/><br/>My quick &amp; simple overall: An entert</span>
  <span id="freeText11397849222933205065" style="display:none">This was one of my favorite Alex Cross books yet. I loved the vampire crime plot! I’m a fantasy&amp; sci-fi book genre fan so it really excited me to read this one. As for the Mastermind crime plot, I was glad it didn’t extend into further books where Alex would not know who the Mastermind was because I feel like that would have became overdone. The suspense of him finding out was just right, in my opinion. It will be interesting to see where he goes career wise. <br /><br />My quick &amp; simple overall: An entertaining, one-sitting installment that kept me up till well after midnight so I could finish it. </span>
