              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/321508-karschtl?shelf=part_of_series">part_of_series</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/321508-karschtl?shelf=crime-thriller-mystery">crime-thriller-mystery</a>, 
