              <span id="reviewTextContainer2228049258" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4639023647405957754">I really enjoyed this book in the Alex Cross series. In this episode, Alex travels to San Francisco to help another detective with a series of brutal murders with vampiric overtones. It was really fun to have the story go back and forth with the POV of Alex and the criminals.</span>

          </span>
